Your variables are outside the login method and they are apparently global variables within your script.
For this reason it will always have the value that input username has at the time of loading the screen.

For this code to work you must either include the variable within the login method:

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-js --&gt;

    function login() {
        var username = document.getElementById(&quot;username&quot;).value;
