    &lt;/form&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

**EDIT:**

As Barmar said you also need to change your button type to &quot;button&quot;. A button inside a form will by default be type &quot;submit&quot;, with that your form will be submited automatically before your validation. So you add the `type=&#39;button&#39;` in the button tag will prevent the form to be submitted automatically. Then you can call the form submit method after the validation like that `document.getElementByTagName(&#39;form&#39;).submit();`

